T18:23:28.000Z","msg":"相信去到今日，部分巴絲已經由一班人一齊參與，到最近開始朋友圈裡面得返自己一個企出嚟。我想趁呢個機會鼓勵一下大家，因為每一個肯企出嚟嘅巴絲都好重要！大家唔好放棄，出到嚟就會有一班理念相同嘅伙伴喺左近。可能有啲巴絲一直都怕單機出嚟所以喺鍵盤發聲，希望你地都可以試下出嚟，唔需要怕！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:00:34.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩，69同616民陣遊行都好啲<br />\n其他行動真係冇撚人出，問親都話今日有嘢做、今日套裝束唔方便、乜乜柒柒<br />\n淨係得一句加油、支持你呢啲打飛機說話"},{"pid":"312dcb7e0bcc44c7eeb460c6fb9fdbe6a510632b","tid":1262603,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:07:13.000Z","msg":"每次都係單機出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想做更多野，想組織一個小隊一齊打下機都好難<br />\n唯有次次都去需要人幫既地方幫下手<br />\n但真係好攰，連續出左黎咁多日靜坐堵塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9309b89a3c59c33baa035f53974cb43b23a7607b","tid":1262603,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"312dcb7e0bcc44c7eeb460c6fb9fdbe6a510632b","tid":1262603,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:07:13.000Z","msg":"每次都係單機出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想做更多野，想組織一個小隊一齊打下機都好難<br />\n唯有次次都去需要人幫既地方幫下手<br />\n但真係好攰，連續出左黎咁多日靜坐堵塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:33:51.000Z","msg":"完全明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />互勉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536a176b76a824ed8efc93157439893c89a2b8a1","tid":1262603,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9309b89a3c59c33baa035f53974cb43b23a7607b","tid":1262603,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"312dcb7e0bcc44c7eeb460c6fb9fdbe6a510632b","tid":1262603,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T06:07:13.000Z","msg":"每次都係單機出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" c